## ðŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project presents an end-to-end **Power BI analysis of UK railway operations**, focusing on revenue performance, passenger journeys, delays, and refunds.  
The dashboard is designed for **executive-level monitoring and operational insights**, enabling stakeholders to identify high-performing routes, delay drivers, and revenue leakage due to refunds.

