- **Refund Rate:** ~5%

---

## ðŸ“ˆ Analytical Coverage

### Revenue & Profitability Analysis
- Revenue and Net Revenue trends by **month**, **ticket type**, and **ticket class**
- Identification of **top 5 revenue-generating rail routes**
- Analysis of **most and least profitable departure stations**
- Profit per trip comparison across major routes

### Operational Performance
- Journey status breakdown: **On Time, Delayed, Cancelled**
- Trip volume distribution by **day of week** and **time slots**
- Peak travel periods (6 PM observed as highest traffic hour)
- Route-wise delay minutes analysis

### Refund & Delay Insights
- Refund revenue by **delay reason** (technical issues, staffing, signal failure, traffic, weather)
- Refund-heavy routes and stations
- Relationship between delays and refund volume

### Passenger & Ticket Behavior
- Revenue split by **ticket class** (Standard vs First Class)
- Ticket type performance (Advance, Anytime, Off-Peak)
- Purchase channel analysis (Online vs Station)
- Railcard-based journey patterns (Adult, Senior, Disabled)

